    style as Normal

Process called "create_no_marker" returns Marker:
    Return Marker with:
    symbol as Circle
    size as 0.0
    edge_width as 0.0
    edge_color as create_black_color()
    fill_color as create_black_color()

Process called "create_circle_marker" returns Marker:
